#: ../../modules/digital/digital.rst:279
msgid ""
"Create a style object to control theme, fonts, spacing, DPI, labels, and "
"more. Passing this object to "
":meth:`~qilisdk.digital.circuit.Circuit.draw` overrides the library "
"defaults for this call. You can also change if the order of the draw "
